# Known CVEs — pre-existing vulnerabilities acknowledged by the team
# Lines starting with # are comments. Other lines are grep patterns
# matched against pnpm audit output to exclude known issues.
# Last reviewed: 2026-04-09

# Vite dev server vulnerabilities (dev-only, not production risk)
Vite.*server\.fs\.deny
Vite.*Arbitrary File Read

# basic-ftp CRLF injection (transitive dep via puppeteer)
basic-ftp.*CRLF
